one_reviews_text: I hope they add more locations and song options. It's a little limited on songs with basically one song with different transitions " bass line, melody, drums, ..." per map with just 2 maps. So you will probably be sick of the songs after a few play throughs but you have a bunch of other things going on at the party to play with.  It is a awesome feeling when you get the party going and is worth every penny!

If you like club sounds, don´t miss this !
very nice job guys ! it´s expandable, so stay tuned, 
maybe with further locations and sounds ;-)
